 but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Robert Burnell was born on 5 May 1450, in Balgriffin, County Dublin, Ireland, his father, Robert John Burnell, was 28 and his mother, Mrs. Robert Burnell, was 25. He had at least 1 son and 1 daughter with lady Margaret Holywood. He died in 1530, in his hometown, at the age of 80."},"et":{"5 May 1450–1530":"5. mai 1450–1530","1450–1530":"1450–1530","1455–1532":"1455–1532","1475–1532":"10.jaanuar1475kuni9.jaanuar1476–1532","1477–Male":"1477–Surnud","1422–Male":"1422–Surnud","1425–Female":"1425–Surnud","1425":"1425","1422":"1422","1477":"1477","1532":"1532","1455":"1455","1475":"10. jaanuar 1475 kuni 9. jaanuar 1476","1530":"1530","about 1477":"umbes 1477","5 May 1450":"5. mai 1450","1450":"1450","Balgriffin, County Dublin, Ireland":"Balgriffin, County Dublin, Iirimaa"},"fi":{"5 May 1450–1530":"5. toukokuuta 1450–1530","1450–1530":"1450–1530","1455–1532":"1455–1532","1475–1532":"vuodesta10.tammikuuta1475vuoteen9.tammikuuta1476–1532","1477–Male":"1477–Kuollut","1422–Male":"1422–Kuollut","1425–Female":"1425–Kuollut","1425":"1425","1422":"1422","1477":"1477","1532":"1532","1455":"1455","1475":"vuodesta 10. tammikuuta 1475 vuoteen 9. tammikuuta 1476","1530":"1530","about 1477":"noin 1477","5 May 1450":"5. toukokuuta 1450","1450":"1450","Balgriffin, County Dublin, Ireland":"Balgriffin, County Dublin, Irlanti"},"fr":{"5 May 1450–1530":"5 mai 1450–1530","1450–1530":"1450–1530","1455–1532":"1455–1532","1475–1532":"du10janvier1475au9janvier1476–1532","1477–Male":"1477–Décédé","1422–Male":"1422–Décédé","1425–Female":"1425–Décédée","1425":"1425","1422":"1422","1477":"1477","1532":"1532","1455":"1455","1475":"du 10 janvier 1475 au 9 janvier 1476","1530":"1530","about 1477":"environ 1477","5 May 1450":"5 mai 1450","1450":"1450","Balgriffin, County Dublin, Ireland":"Balgriffin, County Dublin, Irlande","lifeSummary":"Lo